plot: After shooting and killing a suspect, Toby struggles with PTSD as the IIB tries to stop an assassination.

While going under for emergency surgery, Toby picks up on a man's plan to assassinate a french national. Having alerted the team to investigate it, Toby begins to crumble from having shot and killed a man, confronting an armed suspect with uncharacteristic death wish behavior. Toby sees the bureau therapist as his team narrows in on the assassin.—statmanjeff
